        <item>Q1: The name of which companion of Prophet PBUH (Sahabi) is written in Holy Quran?</item>
        <item>A. Hazrat Hamza R.A</item>
        <item>B. Hazrat Zaid bin Haris R.A</item>
        <item>C. Hazrat Rehman bin Auf R.A</item>
        <item>D. Hazrat Usman R.A</item>
        <item>B</item>

        <item>Q2: Who wrote Muqadimah-ibn-i-Salah?</item>
        <item>A. Imam Ibn-i-Salah</item>
        <item>B. Imam Sakhavi</item>
        <item>C. Imam Nawavi</item>
        <item>D. None of these</item>
        <item>A</item>

        <item>Q3: Who was first to arrange and write the Quran on paper and compiled it in the form of book?</item>
        <item>A. Hazrat Umar (R.A)</item>
